snippet.title: Best VGM 698 - Shin Megami Tensei Nocturne - Musubi
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 123 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N-BiX7QXE8k

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Shin Megami Tensei Nocturne (2004)
Musubi
Shoji Meguro
